## Login with password and change it

## Config in client

```
vim ~/.ssh/config
```
Add following:
```
Host DigitalOcean
HostName 111.236.179.21
User root
```
## Login with key

```
ssh-copy-id DigitalOcean
ssh DigitalOcean
vim /etc/ssh/sshd_config
```
change `PermitRootLogin yes` to `PermitRootLogin without-password`
```
service ssh restart
```
